%3Esucceeding%20in%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eafter%20over%2015%20years%20in%20the%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227358ffb6-5b5b-4fef-a7ab-c0be159702d5%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E1)%20Don't%20assume%20you%20need%20a%20Ph.D.%20to%20do%20cutting-edge%20AI%20work%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EProfessor%20and%20research%20scientist%20roles%20in%20AI%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Emight%20list%20a%20Ph.D.%20as%20a%20requirement%2C%20but%20there%20are%20other%20cutting-edge%20jobs%20in%20this%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20good%20reasons%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faws-ai-scientist-not-too-late-get-phd-ai-amazon-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edo%20a%20Ph.D%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20if%20you%20want%20to%20work%20in%20academia%20or%20explore%20certain%20ideas.%20But%20if%20your%20end%20goal%20is%20doing%20interesting%20AI%20work%20and%20learning%20how%20the%20sausage%20is%20made%2C%20you%20could%20spend%20those%20five%20to%20six%20years%20at%20startups%20or%20big%20labs%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20also%20try%20side%20projects%2C%20making%20use%20of%20open%20source%20code%20and%20online%20communities%20to%20get%20your%20hands%20dirty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20keep%20putting%20in%20the%20time%20and%20effort%20to%20whatever%20you're%20doing%2C%20you'll%20be%20able%20to%20stand%20out%2C%20and%20you'll%20also%20have%20learned%20a%20bunch%20of%20skills%20along%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20the%20perception%20that%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-ai-team-too-late-phd-ai-hype-jad-tarifi-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPh.D%20is%20necessary%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20this%20industry%20has%20changed%20over%20time.%20We%20don't%20take%20them%20into%20consideration%20much%20when%20hiring%20at%20Yutori%2C%20where%20we're%20trying%20to%20build%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-salesforce-struggles-agentforce-flagship-ai-agent-wars-benioff-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20agents%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20can%20help%20people%20with%20digital%20chores%2C%20like%20looking%20for%20apartments%20or%20buying%20headphones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22663%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Parikh%20posing%20with%20the%20other%20two%20founders%20of%20Yutori.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69284ac7abd5e944effba3ac%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20co-founders%20of%20Yutori%20(From%20left%20to%20right%3A%20Abhishek%20Das%2C%20Devi%20Parikh%2C%20and%20Dhruv%20Batra)%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Yutori%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20we%20look%20for%20people%20with%20relevant%20experience%2C%20such%20as%20in%20training%20models%2C%20and%20how%20candidates%20perform%20in%20technical%20interviews%20involving%20coding%20problems%20and%20system%20design%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d789ef1a-ddd3-4b85-9c9c-2a5b1fee9c42%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E2)%20Keep%20your%20professional%20identity%20flexible%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBetween%202011%20and%202013%2C%20there%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bdeep%20learning%20wave%2C%26quot%3B%20when%20the%20AI%20community%20began%20to%20realize%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20deep%20neural%20networks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20fellow%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eresearchers%20tied%20their%20identity%20to%20the%20tools%20they%20had%20worked%20with%20and%20were%20hesitant%20to%20transition%20to%20deep%20models%2C%20even%20though%20it%20was%20clear%20they%20worked%20much%20better%20for%20the%20problems%20we%20were%20addressing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20field%20evolves%20rapidly%2C%20and%20if%20evidence%20tells%20you%20new%20tools%20work%20better%2C%20don't%20hold%20onto%20your%20past%20tool%20set.%20Holding%20on%20to%20your%20professional%20identity%2C%20such%20as%20by%20seeing%20yourself%20only%20as%20an%20academic%2C%20can%20also%20be%20detrimental.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20learned%20not%20to%20hold%20on%20to%20research%20areas.%20I%20worked%20on%20computer%20vision%20during%20my%20Ph.D%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethen%20multimodal%20problems%2C%20and%20later%20generative%20models%20for%20images%20and%20videos.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20I%20didn't%20know%20ChatGPT%20was%20coming%2C%20and%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fscammed-internet-provider-lower-my-bill-deepfakes-ai-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egenerative%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20would%20suddenly%20become%20a%20high%20priority%20in%20tech.%20If%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI'd%20held%20onto%20my%20identity%20as%20a%20computer%20vision%20researcher%20without%20exploring%20these%20other%20things%2C%20I%20would've%20missed%20out%20on%20opportunities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227a3103c4-cafc-4f30-9f27-72f2021cd5d2%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E3)%20Pursue%20your%20genuine%20interests%2C%20not%20what%20you%20think%20you%20should%20do%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20paper%2C%20my%20job%20at%20Meta%20was%20amazing%2C%20and%20you%20probably%20wouldn't%20leave%20it%20to%20start%20a%20company%20if%20you%20were%20being%20strategic%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Femployee-moved-desk-in-office-promotion-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emoving%20up%20in%20your%20career%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20knew%20the%20success%20rate%20of%20startups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20be%20unclear%20whether%20an%20opportunity%20is%20the%20right%20move%20strategically%2C%20but%20I%20find%20it%20easy%20to%20put%20time%20and%20effort%20into%20things%20I%20think%20will%20be%20fun%2C%20and%20produce%20better%20quality%20work%20that%20gets%20recognized.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224e77fbc7-76ac-4a1e-a50e-443a438e21dd%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E4)%20Follow%20through%20on%20ideas%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESeeing%20things%20through%20to%20the%20end%20%E2%80%94%20100%25%2C%20