20the%20author%20and%20her%20son.%20On%20the%20left%2C%20they're%20at%20a%20pumpkin%20patch%2C%20smiling%20with%20a%20pumpkin%2C%20and%20on%20the%20right%20the%20author's%20son%20is%20eating%20pie%20for%20breakfast.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6904c97fc007ca8c273801c2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20and%20her%20son%20have%20been%20eating%20pie%20for%20breakfast%20on%20Thanksgiving%20for%2010%20years.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Ashley%20Archambault%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EWhen%20I%20was%20growing%20up%2C%20my%20grandmother%20always%20suggested%20having%20pie%20for%20breakfast%20on%20Thanksgiving.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWe%20never%20did%20it%20then%2C%20but%20I%20always%20wanted%20to%2C%20and%20I%20finally%20tried%20it%20with%20my%20son%20when%20he%20was%202.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWe%20loved%20it%20so%20much%20that%20we've%20done%20it%20ever%20since%2C%20and%20it's%20our%20favorite%20holiday%20tradition.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%2C%20my%20grandmother%20would%20always%20say%20we%20should%20have%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhich-thanksgiving-pie-do-americans-like-best-apple-vs-pumpkin-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThanksgiving%20pies%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20breakfast.%20I%20thought%20it%20was%20such%20a%20good%20idea%2C%20because%20by%20the%20time%20you're%20done%20eating%20dinner%2C%20you're%20really%20too%20full%20for%20dessert.%20My%20family%20never%20ended%20up%20going%20through%20with%20it%2C%20but%20the%20idea%20stuck%20with%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20had%20my%20son%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20start%20our%20own%20holiday%20traditions%20together.%20I%20remembered%20the%20idea%20of%20having%20pie%20for%20breakfast%20and%20decided%20to%20try%20it.%20In%20order%20for%20the%20pie%20to%20be%20ready%20on%20Thanksgiving%20morning%2C%20I%20had%20to%20stay%20up%20the%20Wednesday%20night%20before%20to%20make%20everything.%20I%20thought%20an%20apple%20pie%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhich-famous-chef-has-the-best-pumpkin-pie-recipe%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epumpkin%20pie%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20fresh%20whipped%20cream%20would%20be%20perfect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227b652404-d900-43fc-a6e5-ebbe672bdbf0%5C%22%3EIt%20went%20so%20well%20the%20first%20year%2C%20and%20we%20added%20on%20to%20the%20tradition%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20son%20was%20only%202%20years%20old%20the%20first%20year%20we%20tried%20it%2C%20so%20it%20was%20his%20first%20time%20trying%20everything.%20After%20I%20put%20him%20to%20bed%2C%20I%20stayed%20up%20cooking%2C%20while%20the%20SNL%20Thanksgiving%20special%20played%20on%20TV%20in%20the%20background.%20It%20all%20felt%20just%20right%20for%20me%2C%20as%20if%20I%20were%20figuring%20out%20the%20kind%20of%20holiday%20I%20wanted%20to%20have%2C%20not%20just%20for%20my%20son%2C%20but%20for%20myself%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20wasn't%20easy%20putting%20everything%20away%20for%20the%20next%20morning%20without%20taste-tasting%2C%20but%20it%20felt%20so%20much%20more%20special%20to%20wait%20for%20Thanksgiving.%20When%20we%20woke%20up%20the%20next%20morning%2C%20I%20put%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmacys-thanksgiving-day-parade-photos-2017-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMacy's%20Thanksgiving%20Day%20Parade%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20right%20away.%20I%20didn't%20even%20feel%20too%20bad%20about%20letting%20us%20eat%20pie%20for%20breakfast%2C%20because%20it%20was%20homemade%20and%20still%20full%20of%20apples%20and%20pumpkin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20son%20looked%20at%20me%20as%20if%20I%20had%20made%20a%20mistake%2C%20but%20when%20I%20reassured%20him%20to%20go%20ahead%20and%20try%20it%2C%20he%20loved%20it.%20I%20had%20my%20pie%20with%20coffee%2C%20while%20he%20had%20his%20with%20milk.%20Although%20it%20was%20delicious%2C%20I%20think%20what%20made%20us%20most%20happy%20was%20being%20together%20and%20doing%20something%20out%20of%20the%20ordinary.%20Before%20the%20morning%20was%20even%20over%2C%20I%20knew%20this%20was%20going%20to%20be%20something%20we%20did%20forever.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a66d0ef1-00a5-4b3b-b250-0860d8d95bfe%5C%22%3EHaving%20pie%20for%20breakfast%20came%20with%20benefits%20I%20couldn't%20have%20predicted%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20establishing%20our%20tradition%20of%20having%20pie%20for%20breakfast%2C%20I%20also%20developed%20a%20special%20Thanksgiving%20coffee%20that%20morning%20by%20putting%20whipped%20cream%20in%20a%20mug%20first%20and%20then%20pouring%20hot%20coffee%20over%20it%2C%20creating%20something%20like%20a%20cappuccino.%20While%20I%20knew%20eating%20traditional%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feasy-thanksgiving-desserts-that-arent-pumpkin-pie-2021-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThanksgiving%20desserts%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20breakfast%20with%20my%20son%20to%20be%20fun%2C%20I%20wasn't%20expecting%20to%20establish%20other%20traditions%20that%20also%20felt%20personal%20and%20resonant%20for%20me%2C%20such%20as%20the%20surprising%20nostalgia%20for%20SNL%20that%20I%20felt%20as%20I%20watched%20the%20special%20(which%20I%20still%20do%20every%20year)%20and%20my%20new%20holiday%20coffee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20my%20son%20also%20spends%20time%20with%20his%20father%20on%20Thanksgiving%2C%20the%20new%20tradition%20has%20had%20some%20unforeseen%20benefits%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fholiday-split-custody-divorce-coparenting-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecoparenting%20over%20the%20holiday%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20too.%20His%20father%20and%20I%20do%20our%20best%20to%20ensure%20that%20our%20son%20sees%20each%20of%20us%20on%20holidays.%20So%2C%20for%20example%2C%20I%20would%20have%20my%20son%20for%20the%20first%20half%20of%20the%20day%2C%20and%20then%20he%20would%20go%20with%20his%20dad%20for%20the%20second%20half.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20hard%20getting%20used%20to%20not%20being%20with%20my%20son%20for%20the%20whole%20day%2C%20but%20it's%20gotten%20easier.%20And%20part%20of%20that%20is%20because%20I%20found%20ways%20to%20make%20our%20holiday%20time%20together%20feel%20full.%20The%20Thanksgiving%20breakfast%20tradition%20allowed%20me%20to%20celebrate%20with%20my%20son%20and%20not%20feel%20as%20sad%20because%20I%20wasn't%20eating%20dinner%20with%20him%20later%20on.%20I%20think%20it%20helps%20my%20son%20in%20the%20same%20way%2C%20too%2C%20because%20he's%20doing%20something%20equally%20as%20special%20with%20each%20parent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f5cd1f36-54cc-488a-8fac-61cd4d904489%5C%22%3EOur%20pie%20tradition%20has%20become%20the%20best%20part%20of%20Thanksgiving%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20son%20is%2012%20now%2C%20and%20we%20have%20kept%20the%20tradition%20going%20ever%20since.%20When%20I'm%20feeling%20really%20ambitious%2C%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fina-garten-easy-pie-thanksgiving-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emake%20a%20pecan%20pie%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20too.%20When%20I%20remarried%2C%20we%20let%20my%20husband%20in%20on%20the%20ritual%2C%20and%20he%20loves%20it.%20We're%20both%20big%20coffee%20drinkers%2C%20and%20the%20pie%20and%20coffee%20combo%20is%20really%20perfect.%20Everything%20that%20happens%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20Thanksgiving%20after%20pie%20for%20breakfast%20is%20just%20a%20bonus%2C%20because%20we've%20already%20enjoyed%20the%20most%20important%20part%20of%20the%20holiday%20for%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthanksgiving-pie-for-breakfast-family-holiday-tradition-2025-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1764246183000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6904c97fc007ca8c273801c2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fth