20be%20a%20viable%20option%20for%20us.%20We%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F5-star-airbnb-host-things-guests-should-know-before-booking-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edone%20Airbnb%3C%2Fa%3E%20years%20ago%2C%20but%20it%20was%20so%20disruptive%20with%20having%20to%20clean%20the%20entire%20house%20and%20find%20another%20place%20to%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221673%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rob%20Nachbar%20and%20Rae%20Adams%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F691399ee62a04500b316303a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222412%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERob%20Nachbar%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20Rae%20Adams%2C%20have%20been%20renting%20out%20their%20backyard%20for%20years.%3Cp%3ERob%20Nachbar%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20put%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhipcamp-host-rents-backyard-to-campers-rvs-to-make-money-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebackyard%20up%20for%20rent%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20had%20no%20idea%20if%20people%20would%20even%20want%20to%20use%20it.%20Since%20then%2C%20we've%20gotten%20a%20lot%20of%20reservations%2C%20and%20it%20hasn't%20been%20disruptive%20to%20our%20lives%20at%20all.%20It's%20been%20a%20very%20easy%20and%20profitable%20side%20hustle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20call%20our%20backyard%20%26quot%3BPong%20Springs.%26quot%3B%20It%20has%20a%20seven-person%20hot%20tub%2C%20100-inch%20screen%2C%20a%20ping%20pong%20table%2C%20an%20outdoor%20kitchen%20and%20grill%2C%20a%20dart%20board%2C%20and%20gas%20fireplaces.%20We%20rent%20it%20out%20by%20the%20hour%2C%20typically%20starting%20at%20%2475%20per%20hour%20on%20the%20weekends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20guests%20are%20really%20varied.%20We%20just%20had%20a%20couple%20go%20on%20a%20date%20night%20and%20watch%20a%20movie%20in%20the%20hot%20tub.%20One%20week%2C%20we%20had%20a%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstreami